The media project worker.


Features:

- asynchronously search for torrents from multiple sites
- fetch new releases from web sources (vcdquality releases, tvrage schedule, sputnikmusic reviews)
- fetch new media matching releases filters (imdb rating, tvrage style, sputnikmusic rating)
- fetch new media similar/related to the local media (movies directors and actors, music bands)
- fetch movies subtitles
- unpack, clean and sort new media into the media type based directories
- update media metadata from web sources (imdb, tvrage, sputnikmusic)
- retrieve trailers and audio tracks urls for local media and new releases
- sync media to network hosts


Start the worker:
./mediaworker/run.py
